node.text: There are so many types of masks in various gorgeous prints now. Just go invest in one comfy one. I use those clinical white green ones with loops to go around my head, not my ears. My husband prefers the grey N95 ones. My 16 year-old prefers the thin foam ones from Korea (You can get those from Shopee). I customise reusable cloth masks for my 8 and 11 year-olds so, after use, just pop it into the uv steriliser. It does not matter if it is single digit or not. We still not out of the woods.
@mugglefrommasz haha babe u wrote like an essay. Yea I think we'll be wearing masks for a long time.. I really hate it! W specs it just fogs up. ( But I do have a few cloth ones! )

#circuitbreakersg #sgmummies #sgfamily
